text: Lemurs freaking love definite articles. Who'd have guessed?
"Everything for the state, nothing outside the state, nothing against the state" is a solid (if somewhat hyperbolic) definition.

... Honestly think the furry little fuckers sometimes understand The Chaldean Geometry as The, The, The, The, The, The, and that's it. 
(They called me retarded earlier so I'm being cranky.)

Parable of the day.
Nick Land went among the people and said, take these keys to the tongues of the angels. And some among the people took the keys, and, Lo, the angels spoke to them. And the angels said, "Nick Land is Retarded."
Not even my discovery. But it's still not over!
Imagine the action movies that will be based on this.
They get to just memory-hole basically the entirety of history, unfortunately.
Oh sure, totally not the end times.
Imagine that sitting on your lawn at dusk, silently staring.
That's when I woke up screaming.
